name: pocono mtn postcard tee
description:
in one day we designed this thing, had reject burn the screen, and we printed them in joes basement. they make us laugh and will make you popular amongst the entire world. 

there are sort of random colors. small is honey/gray. medium is green/gray. large are tan/dark green. XL is only white. subject to availability.


text reads "greetings from... the greek favourites!"
and then underneath it describes the origin "pocono mountains"
